Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:19.17,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}手繪不佳也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.17,0:01:23.93,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Let me go for my one true belief
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.17,0:01:23.93,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我只會為了追尋那唯一的信念而行動
