Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:35.02,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}To be a knight,to be a light for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:35.02,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}做你的騎士 做你的明燈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.02,0:01:36.46,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We'll be shining bright
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.02,0:01:36.46,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我們會無比閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.46,0:01:37.01,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}No more tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.46,0:01:37.01,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不再需要眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:39.12,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}No more tears,everything works out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:39.12,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不再需要眼淚 我們將不再懼怕任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:41.65,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}That's "God Only Knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:41.65,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}那就是所謂的“只有神知道”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:43.72,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't get me wrong
