Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:43.72,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不要誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:46.11,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}這不是現實中的愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.11,0:01:48.82,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll do anything for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.11,0:01:48.82,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}但我會為你做到一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.82,0:01:51.94,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Whatever happens in my life,turn the page and come of age
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.82,0:01:51.94,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不管人生將會發生什麼 我都將翻過此頁跨上成人的階梯
