Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:57.77,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Try to make my life complete,trust myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:57.77,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}度過自己認可的人生 相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:02:00.40,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Be strong and do my best
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:02:00.40,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}變的堅強 竭盡所能
