Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:13.29,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Find your love…Find your way…For your life…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:13.29,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}為你的人生尋找到愛與歸宿
